    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the funding, the house... all of it. just one bad quarter and the whole thing collapsed. i've spent 10 years building this and now i'm just sitting here looking at millions in debt. i don't even know how to look my family in the eye. i just feel like a complete fraud.",
