      "content": "a therapist? i dont think they can fix this. everything is permanent now. the debt, the ruined reputation, the way everyone is going to look at me. it feels like there's just no way back from this. it's like the version of me that actually mattered is just dead already. there's no \"stepping through\" a loss this big.",
